reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Cables at a great price
reviews.reviewText: I got these to replace some old worn out cables and they are built nice and also charge all devices at max charging speeds. No complaints these work as good as they look.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I can't speak for the power, but they seem durable and work well
reviews.reviewText: I got a fantastic deal on these. I was concerned the oversized ends would not properly couple with the port due to a small opening in the phone case, but they are working just fine, and I have a short cable for data transfer, a medium for charging in place, and a long cable to extend a bit if my battery is low and i need to stay connected. Maybe I should buy another set as a backup.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Well made, robust, high speed and attractive
reviews.reviewText: I got these cables to replace some standard ones that have frayed overtime. I’m a chef and I keep my cords in my day bag and in my kitchen. They get thrown around and are subjected to a lot of abuse from travel and being tossed around/cleared off the prep table when we’re getting ready for service. I’ve put my cords through quite a bit and these in particular have held up better than any that I have used. Very robust construction, very attractive and very unique so that you’re not getting yours confused with others. Priced very fair and would make a great gift for anyone who’s always losing or breaking their cables.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Pleasantly surprised, durable & high quality at low price
reviews.reviewText: Seen marked down due to overstock, at 3 for $5 wasn't really expecting that much just your basic cheap cables that will work fine but aren't very sturdy/durable. Time will tell as I've just received them but they seem much more durable than the average charging cord especially at this price. I've seen single cables for $15 that aren't this well built. Will update if they end up not lasting as long as I think they will but so far they've pretty much been the best deal I've ever seen for charging cable.
